EREVISTA ELA , Mulipeleli , ennamucicimiha Yehova Muluku , Mulamuleli a veelaponi .
Ela ennaahakararya achu ni michaka yaphaama yawi moohilekela Omwene wa Muluku wa wirimu onahaala omaliha onanara woothene ni orehererya elapo yavathi ekhale parataiso .
Ela ennateka nroromelo mwa Yesu Kristu , yoowo aakhwile wi hiyaano naakhele okumi woohimala nave yoowo vano onalamulela ntoko Mwene a Omwene wa Muluku .
Erevista ela ennapakiwa moohihiyererya opacerya 1879 nave henavolowela miyaha sa elapo .
Ela erino mathipelo a Piipiliya .
